data.description: STOP THE CAR!! Lots of privacy in a cul-de-sac. Charming, cozy home with 4 bedrooms/bonus room/game room or 5th bedroom. Features an extended driveway for multiple vehicles. The 2 story home features some exciting updates which includes updated bathrooms, updated kitchen with granite counter tops, updated siding and roof, windows, and a tall rail fence with wide gate access for parking an RV, boat or motorcycles. A converted garage can be great for entertaining family and friends. Near military bases and Newport News Shipyard. The seller will pay $5,000 towards closing costs. Bring qualified buyers. A must see!! Seller is motivated!!
